Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Feet MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Effusion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And Localizer is enabled

When I click on the Localizer
And select one part on the Localizer canvas
And close the canvas
Then 'Mild' radio button is enabled
And 'Significant' radio button is enabled
And 'Haemarthros' radio button is enabled
And 'Capsule rupture' radio button is enabled
And 'Loose Fragment' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Capsule rupture' radio button
Then 'Extraarticular articular effusion' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Loose Fragment' checkbox
Then 'Diameter in mm' input field is enabled
